4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper deals with a problem of decision-making under constraints, which is a common theme in AI research. 
5. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics): The paper involves solving a discrete optimization problem of finding an optimal packing of items into a limited-size knapsack.
